menuconfig UART_XLNX_PS
	bool "Xilinx serial driver for MPSoC"
	depends on SOC_FAMILY_ZYNQMP
	select SERIAL_HAS_DRIVER
	help
	  This option enables the UART driver for Xilinx MPSoC
          platforms.
	  Say y if you wish to use serial port on Xilinx MPSoC
          platforms.

